ransport exponent separating Hamiltonian-like and\nfractal random walk-like dynamics, supported through the simulation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Apr 2004 16:59:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 May 2004 10:40:08 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 14 Dec 2004 00:31:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
