i-particles might be\nrelated to bosons with effective spins.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 28 Apr 2004 07:10:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 10 Feb 2007 14:06:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
